Symbol.Script_3D:
! Steam Unit Heater
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
addStatus = 0 IF GLOB_CONTEXT > 40 AND GLOB_CONTEXT < 50 THEN addStatus = 3 ENDIF
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT A/2, dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, dTDepth/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, dTDepth/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -dTDepth/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -dTDepth/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ROTx 90 ADDz -dTDepth/2 EXTRUDE 5, 0, 0, dTDepth, addStatus+16+32, -A/2, 0, 0, A/2, 0, 0, A/2, ZZYZX, 0, -A/2, ZZYZX, 0, -A/2, 0, -1 POLY_ 7, -A/2, 0, 1, A/2, 0, 1, A/2, ZZYZX, 1, -A/2, ZZYZX, 1, -A/2, 0, -1, 0, ZZYZX/2, 901, rr, 360, 4001 ADDz dTDepth POLY_ 10, -A/2, 0, 1, A/2, 0, 1, A/2, ZZYZX, 1, -A/2, ZZYZX, 1, -A/2, 0, -1, -holeWidth/2, ZZYZX/2-holeHeight/2, 1, holeWidth/2, ZZYZX/2-holeHeight/2, 1, holeWidth/2, ZZYZX/2+holeHeight/2, 1, -holeWidth/2, ZZYZX/2+holeHeight/2, 1, -holeWidth/2, ZZYZX/2-holeHeight/2, -1 DEL 3
FOR i = 1 TO num ! --- Louver --- ADD 0, -dTDepth/2, ZZYZX/2+holeHeight/2-0.052*(i-1) PLANE 4, -holeWidth/2, 0, 0, holeWidth/2, 0, 0, holeWidth/2, -0.021, -0.028, -holeWidth/2, -0.021, -0.028 PLANE 4, -holeWidth/2, -0.021, -0.028, holeWidth/2, -0.021, -0.028, holeWidth/2, -0.025, -0.04, -holeWidth/2, -0.025, -0.04 DEL 1 NEXT i
ADD 0, dTDepth/2, ZZYZX/2 ! --- Engine --- MUL A/0.42, (B-dTDepth-0.025)/0.37, A/0.42 ROTx -90 FOR j = 1 TO 4 ROTz 90*j ADD 0, 0.01, 0.08 ROTx -105 POLY_ 6, 0.015, 0, 1, 0.155, 0, 1, 0.155, 0.06, 1, 0.135, 0.08, 1001, 0.015, 0.08, 1, 0.015, 0, -1 DEL 3 NEXT j
CYLIND 0.09, 0.025 ADDz 0.09 CYLIND 0.23, 0.085 ADD -0.11, 0.085, 0 BLOCK 0.22, 0.005, 0.23 DEL 1 ADDz 0.23 CONE 0.05, 0.085, 0.035, 90, 90 DEL 2
FOR k = 1 TO 2 MULx 1-2*(k-1) ADDx 0.11 ROTz 90 ROTx 90 PRISM_ 18, 0.01, -0.17, 0, 15, -0.16, 0, 15, -0.16, 0.09, 15, 0.16, 0.09, 15, 0.16, 0, 15, 0.17, 0, 15, 0.17, 0.264, 15, 0.09, 0.32, 15, -0.09, 0.32, 15, -0.17, 0.264, 15, -0.17, 0, -1, -0.08685, 0.31, 15, 0.08685, 0.31, 15, 0.16, 0.25878, 15, 0.16, 0.1, 15, -0.16, 0.1, 15, -0.16, 0.25878, 15, -0.08685, 0.31, -1 DEL 4 NEXT k DEL 3 ELSE ADD -A/2, -dTDepth/2, 0 BLOCK A, dTDepth, ZZYZX DEL 1
ADD -holeWidth/2, -dTDepth/2-0.025, ZZYZX/2-holeHeight/2 BLOCK holeWidth, 0.025, holeHeight ! --- Louver --- DEL 1
ADD 0, dTDepth/2, ZZYZX/2 ! --- Engine --- MUL A/0.42, (B-dTDepth-0.025)/0.37, A/0.42 ROTx -90 ADDz 0.32 CONE 0.05, 0.085, 0.035, 90, 90 DEL 1
ROTz 90 ROTx 90 ADDz -0.12 PRISM_ 7, 0.24, -0.17, 0, 15, 0.17, 0, 15, 0.17, 0.264, 15, 0.09, 0.32, 15, -0.09, 0.32, 15, -0.17, 0.264, 15, -0.17, 0, -1 DEL 6 ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 15, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 15 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Steam Unit Heater
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 A/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -holeWidth/2, -dTDepth/2-0.025, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 holeWidth/2, -dTDepth/2-0.025, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT A/2, dTDepth/2, 1, -A/2, dTDepth/2, 1, -A/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, A/2, -dTDepth/2, 1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT holeWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, ! --- Louver --- -holeWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, -holeWidth/2, -dTDepth/2-0.025, 1, holeWidth/2, -dTDepth/2-0.025, 1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
ADD2 0, dTDepth/2 MUL2 A/0.42, (B-dTDepth-0.025)/0.37
HOTSPOT2 -0.035, 0.37, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0.035, 0.37, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -0.12, 0.32, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0.12, 0.32, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT -0.12, 0, 1, ! --- Engine --- 0.12, 0, 1, 0.12, 0.32, 1, 0.085, 0.32, 1, 0.035, 0.37, 1, -0.035, 0.37, 1, -0.085, 0.32, 1, -0.12, 0.32, 1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
LINE2 -0.085, 0.32, 0.085, 0.32
DEL 2 ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 5, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 5 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Steam Unit Heater
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
rr = 0.16*(A/0.42) holeWidth = A-0.12 num = INT((ZZYZX-0.20)/0.052) IF ((ZZYZX-0.20) MOD 0.05) > 0.0251 THEN num = num+1 holeHeight = num*0.052
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z

IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF

ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
